00037 /* Version information is made available at compile time in two forms:
00038 ** 1) a version string for printing
00039 ** 2) a combined SDK version and build number, suitable for comparisons
00040 **    to determine what SDK version is being used.
00041 **    SDK 1.2.3 build 567 => 102030567
00042 **    Note that 2 digits are used for each version number, so that:
00043 **     1.9.0  == 01.09.00 < 01.10.00 == 1.10.0 
00044 **     10.9.0 == 10.09.00 > 09.10.00 == 9.10.0 
00045 ** 
00046 */ 
00047 #define OCTEON_SDK_VERSION_NUM  501000609ull
00048 #define OCTEON_SDK_VERSION_STRING   "Cavium Inc. OCTEON SDK version 5.1.0, build 609"
